According to Chinese media, Li Hongzhi once reimbursed 73 medical expenses for himself and his daughter in this unit, and there are 73 existing receipts, with a total amount of 219.71 yuan. Among them, there are 48 receipts for Li Hongzhi's own medical expenses, amounting to 129.6 yuan. 

These documents show that Li Hongzhi himself has been treated in 7 hospitals including Changchun City Hospital, City People's Hospital, PLA Changchun 208 Hospital, and Chaoyang District Traditional Chinese Medicine Hospital.
   
